We started Lynch Dental Center over 20 years ago and we've grown as a family-owned practice, one patient and one family at a time.  Today we continue to value our relationships with each patient as we provide personal dental care to each individual. 

We have two dental centers, one in Chicago and one in River Forest. You are welcome to make appointments in the office that is most convenient for you. 

Whether a patient is looking for a dental practice for themselves, their family, or is in need of emegency care, our staff is experienced and highly trained in all aspects of patient services.

We have two dental centers, one in Chicago and one in River Forest. You are welcome to make appointments in the office that is most convenient for you.

organization_short_description:
Our downtown Chicago dental practice prides itself on having spanned three generations. Dr. Greg Strobel Sr. opened Strobel Dentistry in this location in 1932 and practiced here for 50 years. He served as the Chicago Blackhawks general dentist for two decades. Dr. Greg Strobel Jr. joined his father in the practice in 1975 and practiced through 2013 with his son, Dr. Dan Strobel, who started in 2005. Dr. Dan now practices with Dr. Isabella Terrassa, who joined the office in November 2013.

Throughout the decades, we have built a stellar reputation for offering leading-edge, ethical dentistry, designed to meet the needs and busy schedules of our patients. organization_seo_description: At Strobel Dentistry, our qualified Chicago dentist Dr. Dan Strobel offers quality dental treatment in downtown Chicago, IL. Schedule your appointment today!
organization_short_description:
Our downtown Chicago dental practice prides itself on having spanned three generations. Dr. Greg Strobel Sr. opened Strobel Dentistry in this location in 1932 and practiced here for 50 years. He served as the Chicago Blackhawks general dentist for two decades. Dr. Greg Strobel Jr. joined his father in the practice in 1975 and practiced through 2013 with his son, Dr. Dan Strobel, who started in 2005. Dr. Dan now practices with Dr. Isabella Terrassa, who joined the office in November 2013.

Throughout the decades, we have built a stellar reputation for offering leading-edge, ethical dentistry, designed to meet the needs and busy schedules of our patients. Each member of our team is committed, from extensive continuing education and the use of the latest technology, to ensuring high-quality clinical care and providing welcoming, responsive, and accommodating customer service. We strive to establish confidence and trust with our patients through honest treatment presentation and accessible finance options.
